data.description: Spacious single-level living with tons of upgrades to include engineered hardwood flooring throughout, screened-in porch, curb appeal, and rock-landscaped yard. Convenient to Anderson's dining, entertainment, and healthcare facilities. The 4th bedroom is currently being used as a home office. The property is 3.5 miles from I-85. USDA is eligible. Come visit Anderson County, Clemson and Anderson University, Lake Hartwell, golf courses, and its own booming downtown area with dining, lofts, concerts, and outdoor markets in the summertime.
